1
00:00:52,330 --> 00:00:52,790
Lin Yan,

2
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:53,900
drag her into the passage.

3
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:54,360
Zhou Fu,

4
00:00:54,530 --> 00:00:55,530
get down and roll.

5
00:01:09,830 --> 00:01:11,460
They really want to burn us to death.

6
00:01:11,460 --> 00:01:12,130
Lord Shen,

7
00:01:12,430 --> 00:01:13,260
what do we do?

8
00:01:13,460 --> 00:01:14,260
This map marks

9
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:14,660
a secret passage.

10
00:01:14,660 --> 00:01:15,960
Go 30 zhang ahead in this passage,

11
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:16,500
there is a fork.

12
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:17,830
The left leads to the rockery in the abandoned garden,

13
00:01:17,830 --> 00:01:19,360
the right leads to the back alley of the Penal Case Department.

14
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,430
The fire is hard to put out.

15
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:21,460
The smoke will rise.

16
00:01:21,460 --> 00:01:22,660
We must leave immediately.

17
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:23,120
My lord,

18
00:01:23,230 --> 00:01:24,630
there must be an ambush outside.

19
00:01:24,630 --> 00:01:26,030
They expect us to die.

20
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,820
If we catch them off guard,

21
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,720
we might have a chance to survive.

22
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:49,160
Stepping in the wrong order

23
00:01:49,160 --> 00:01:51,420
will trigger pit traps or poison arrows.

24
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:54,060
Follow my steps closely.

25
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,360
Only step on the normal-colored slabs.

26
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:12,360
The core of the formation is here.

27
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:27,460
We passed it.

28
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:35,060
Fragments of Blood Chalcedony.

29
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:38,000
Someone carried the chalcedony through here

30
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,200
and had a struggle.

31
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,260
Was it Prefect Gu?

32
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,130
Miss Xiaocui,

33
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,460
have you seen anyone carrying

34
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:49,700
this red jade

35
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,160
pass by here?

36
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,490
Robbed the jade.

37
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,060
Black clothes.

38
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,030
Let me go. Let me go.

39
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:12,830
So many black...

40
00:03:15,330 --> 00:03:15,830
My lord,

41
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:16,329
I...

42
00:03:16,329 --> 00:03:17,230
I remember now.

43
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:19,030
Lord Sizheng seemed to mention before

44
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,560
that Prefect Gu was corrupt

45
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:22,430
and went missing due to enemies seeking revenge.

46
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,960
Maybe it was those men in black.

47
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,160
If it was for revenge,

48
00:03:25,329 --> 00:03:26,600
why use drugs to control them?

49
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,400
Why go to such lengths to fake supernatural events

50
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,230
and steal corpses?

51
00:03:29,230 --> 00:03:30,829
And why reappear seven years later

52
00:03:30,829 --> 00:03:32,630
to hunt down the investigators?

53
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:48,590
Nine-Turn Reincarnation Formation.

54
00:04:12,100 --> 00:04:12,900
Shen Mo.

55
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,700
You trespassed in a forbidden area,

56
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:15,560
committed arson and burned corpses,

57
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,800
and took witnesses hostage.

58
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,029
I now act in the name of

59
00:04:18,029 --> 00:04:19,029
the Director of the Penal Case Department.

60
00:04:19,029 --> 00:04:20,100
Arrest him.

61
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:21,089
Uncle Zhou.

62
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,700
If you wanted to arrest me,

63
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:24,560
why wait until I escaped from the secret passage?

64
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,020
You knew this exit was here

65
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:27,700
and waited specifically for me, right?

66
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:29,360
Your right hand in your sleeve

67
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,500
has been clenched tight.

68
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,760
You are squeezing your son's

69
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,220
peace amulet, aren't you?

70
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,260
Uncle Zhou.

71
00:04:35,930 --> 00:04:37,659
They used your son to force you.

72
00:04:38,130 --> 00:04:40,100
Forced you to kill me here, right?

73
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:44,890
Traitor,

74
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:46,159
die!

75
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:48,659
Go.

76
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,830
Qin Muzhi wants the Blood Chalcedony.

77
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:53,030
There are horses at the end of the alley.

78
00:04:53,930 --> 00:04:55,030
The traitors are fierce.

79
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:55,800
Arrest them!

80
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,860
Go to the end of the alley.

81
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,330
Registrar Shen,

82
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,660
why in such a hurry?

83
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:17,330
I am Qin Muzhi.

84
00:05:17,530 --> 00:05:19,530
I've long heard of your brilliant deduction skills.

85
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:20,600
I came today

86
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:21,860
to ask you

87
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:23,190
to hand something over.

88
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:27,760
What do you want, Lord Qin?

89
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,600
The Blood Chalcedony

90
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,730
obtained from the mortuary.

91
00:05:29,730 --> 00:05:31,660
This item is related to an old case.

92
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:33,700
It must be sealed and reviewed by the Ministry of Justice.

93
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,360
An old case?

94
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,230
Are you referring to Gu Wenyuan's disappearance in Yunzhou?

95
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:37,159
I recall that

96
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:38,700
the files for this case were empty

97
00:05:38,700 --> 00:05:39,659
and have long been sealed.

98
00:05:39,659 --> 00:05:41,159
Demanding evidence now

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,060
violates protocol.

100
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:42,960
Extraordinary times

101
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:43,860
call for extraordinary measures.

102
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:44,630
Registrar Shen,

103
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:45,700
do you know this Blood Chalcedony

104
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:46,830
is no ordinary jade?

105
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,230
It is one of the cores

106
00:05:48,230 --> 00:05:49,030
of the Nine-Turn Reincarnation Formation.

107
00:05:49,030 --> 00:05:49,760
Gathering all seven

108
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,830
can set up a heaven-defying formation.

109
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:52,860
Keeping such an evil item

110
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,330
will inevitably cause disasters.

111
00:05:54,330 --> 00:05:56,530
You know so much about the formation, Lord Qin.

112
00:05:56,530 --> 00:05:57,659
Just a little.

113
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,400
Rumor has it

114
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,100
it can lock souls,

115
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:02,000
and even

116
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:03,500
reverse life and death.

117
00:06:03,500 --> 00:06:04,460
Back then, Gu Wenyuan

118
00:06:04,460 --> 00:06:05,760
was obsessed with this

119
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,400
and brought disaster upon himself.

120
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,330
Registrar Shen,

121
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:09,530
do not

122
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:11,460
follow in his footsteps.

123
00:06:12,030 --> 00:06:13,260
Qin Muzhi holds a high position,

124
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,760
yet he came to rob the evidence himself.

125
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:16,430
He knows the formation so well.

126
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,200
The beast-faced man

127
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,030
and Zhou Yan being coerced

128
00:06:18,030 --> 00:06:20,000
all point to a massive power behind him.

129
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,400
Since you wanted the chalcedony, Lord Qin,

130
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,230
why didn't you send someone earlier

131
00:06:24,230 --> 00:06:25,400
to retrieve it from the mortuary,

132
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,600
instead of letting it fall into my hands?

133
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,230
Then going through all the trouble to hunt me down,

134
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:30,030
lay an ambush,

135
00:06:30,260 --> 00:06:31,530
and force Director Zhou?

136
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:32,330
In that case,

137
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,860
I definitely cannot let you live.

138
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,460
Jump into the well.

139
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,060
Help me.

140
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:56,530
Guard all exits.

141
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,530
They will either drown,

142
00:06:59,300 --> 00:06:59,930
or

143
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:02,200
come out from there.

144
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:05,660
That place

145
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:08,900
holds Gu Wenyuan's true secret.
